Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.01,OP6,,0,0,0,,OP Start
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:16.00,OP6,,0,0,0,,Hey boys, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:20.60,OP6,,0,0,0,,Humans aren't such a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:25.44,OP6,,0,0,0,,Who needs tomorrow anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:28.71,OP6,,0,0,0,,so don't hide your fists
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:32.92,OP6,,0,0,0,,You're not old enough
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:39.29,OP6,,0,0,0,,to sell your dreams away to uncertainty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:44.66,OP6,,0,0,0,,Hey boys, you're the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:48.26,OP6,,0,0,0,,who can pull the trigger in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:51.64,OP6,,0,0,0,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.64,0:00:54.64,OP6,,0,0,0,,We're living in this senseless, ridiculous,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:59.01,OP6,,0,0,0,,awesome world right at this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:01.48,OP6,,0,0,0,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:07.35,OP6,,0,0,0,,Don't forget every truth or lie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:11.08,OP6,,0,0,0,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:13.42,OP6,,0,0,0,,We're way too young to die
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:18.29,OP6,,0,0,0,,In this empty town lined with empty faces
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.29,0:01:20.56,OP6,,0,0,0,,All the kids took off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:23.10,OP6,,0,0,0,,into this windless night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:29.00,OP6,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,3000)}Because they want to change something
Comment: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:31.07,OP6,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:37.70,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\blur4\fad(600,600)\pos(681,556)\3c&H000000&}Conclusion\Nin the Rain of Tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,By special...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,By special,\Nyou meant that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like I'm gonna lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If they continue to be released\Nfor a long period of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse Marks will progressively\Neat your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When they have entirely\Neaten you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you will lose yourself... forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This body...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like there's no time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any feeling\Nin my left arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That power you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,seems to involve\Nsome risks too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is called the Valley of the End.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:05:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is the perfect stage,\Ndon't you think... Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I said there'd be\Nno more talking, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case,\Nhow about we bring it to a close...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All our battles up to now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Next for Squad Seven.\NUzumaki Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruno Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yipeee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,With Naruto...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And Uchiha Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yipeee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,With Sasuke...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Try not to slow me down, loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but... but... you told us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they......
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we a three-man squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! We three are one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?\NScaredy Cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... are you hurt?\NScaredy Cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You are one of the ones\NI want to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I want... to fight you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see\Nany more deaths
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of my precious comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Summoning Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I... will protect Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's funny, believe it!\NI'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think I can finally\Nbeat you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!\NDon't talk foolish, you failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to be\Na failure forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just bring it, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Put on your headband before that!\NI'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't even be able\Nto put one wound on my forehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying this is a testament
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to fighting on equal terms\Nas a Leaf Shinobi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll win no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't flatter yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And from this time onward...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Chidori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Rasengan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rasengan!\N- Chidori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Chidori!\N- Rasengan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This Chakra...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's started to rain!\NWill it erase the scent?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already close.\NThis way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I too late...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did things come to this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Sasuke's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't make it in time...\Nplease forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the kind of person you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have made\Na desperate effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,With me, you're all\Nyour father talks about...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my one and only brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I will continue to be for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,a wall that you must find\Na way to cross over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you were to hate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You are someone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,who can obtain Mangekyo Sharingan\Njust like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,However, on one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your closest friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Valley of the End...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,T o think that Sasuke and Naruto\Nwould battle it out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How ironic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When I look at\Nthe flow of this water,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it's as if I'm being confronted\Nby an eternal, never-ending battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the fate of the two people\Ndepicted in these statues here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,who founded the Village Hidden\Nin the Leaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto and Sasuke,\Nas long as you both live...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:19:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,your closest friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,abide by anything you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I will get my hands on power\Ndoing it my own way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I will surpass you\Ndoing it my own way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:20:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain's... Iet up, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,With that much rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to pursue\Nthe scent anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto is more important now\Nthan pursuing Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten interesting, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Comment: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:07.43,ED9,,0,0,0,,ED Start
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:17.72,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}When I recalled the parts one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:24.09,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}I felt as though I had understood everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:34.66,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Faded words which I kept so close to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:44.44,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Speechless nights, a hint of warmth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:51.18,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}and this distant yearning for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:22:00.49,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}I live, simply repeating this cycle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:12.20,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Held in my two hands is a droplet of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.65,0:22:22.65,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Softly clutching forgotten memories, lost words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:36.45,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}{\fad(0,2500)}I'll keep these thoughts...
